1. *Poručnik* je nosio zastavu tokom paradnog marša. (The lieutenant was carrying the flag during the parade march.)
2. Malo dete je sa divljenjem gledalo *poručnika*. (The little child was watching the lieutenant with admiration.)
3. *Poručniku* su odlikovanja dodeljena u čast njegovih zasluga. (The lieutenant was awarded decorations in honour of his merits.)
4. *Poručnici* je ponuđeno da preuzme komandu nad vojskom. (The lieutenant was offered to take command of the army.)
5. *Poručniku* je dato naređenje da istraži sumnjivu situaciju. (The lieutenant was given an order to investigate the suspicious situation.)